Subject: [ghostium] Font enumeration + @font-face hook

Spec-G wiring. Anchors at top of two Blink files. The real calls into
``FingerprintNoiseSource::HasFontWhitelist`` /
``FingerprintNoiseSource::FontAllowed`` land at:

  * ``FontManager::query``-style enumeration paths in
    ``font_manager.cc`` (``document.fonts`` iteration, the
    ``window.queryLocalFonts`` Permissions-policy gated API).
  * ``FontFaceSetDocument::CheckFont`` in ``font_face_set_document.cc``
    so that a ``@font-face`` declaration whose ``src: local("X")``
    references a non-whitelisted family fails to match (forcing the
    cascade to the next fallback in the family list).

Generic families (``serif`` / ``sans-serif`` / ``monospace`` /
``cursive`` / ``fantasy`` / ``system-ui`` / ``math`` / ``emoji`` /
``fangsong``) are always allowed; the predicate handles that.

